55:50.173 --> 55:52.641
She used to have this real wild streak.

55:55.846 --> 55:58.337
Hey, Mary, you home?

55:58.382 --> 56:00.111
Mare?

56:01.818 --> 56:03.843
No luck.

56:04.955 --> 56:11.224
I mean, no luck...yet.

56:13.397 --> 56:16.127
You want to come in? You can wait.

56:19.069 --> 56:21.469
This is it. Home sweet home.

56:21.505 --> 56:23.439
I'm upstairs. Mary's down.

56:26.209 --> 56:29.269
This place used to be her mom's.

56:29.312 --> 56:32.042
We had to give it a little personality, though.

56:32.082 --> 56:35.381
LUCY: It was a little...

56:35.419 --> 56:37.284
Oh, what's the word?

56:37.320 --> 56:38.548
DRACULA: Catholic.

56:38.588 --> 56:41.887
Ha! Exactly.

56:41.925 --> 56:46.521
Hey, can I get you some coffee or something?

56:46.563 --> 56:50.124
I don't drink...coffee.

56:52.369 --> 56:55.395
Why don't you make yourself comfortable?

56:56.907 --> 56:59.845
I'll be right back down.

57:00.813 --> 57:02.542
So you haven't told me your name.

57:02.582 --> 57:04.209
DRACULA: I have many.

57:06.185 --> 57:09.848
But we're all so much more complicated...

57:09.889 --> 57:12.585
than our names.

57:12.625 --> 57:15.059
I...

57:15.094 --> 57:18.757
Yes, Lucy?

57:18.798 --> 57:22.700
I was named after the Peanuts character.

58:11.708 --> 58:13.903
GIRL: Mary. Hey, there was a guy in here.

58:13.944 --> 58:16.412
MARY: Where's Lucy? Have you seen her?

58:16.446 --> 58:20.007
GIRL: She cut out early. Looked like she had a date.

58:20.050 --> 58:21.347
Why, what's the problem?

58:21.384 --> 58:23.045
Problem?

58:24.487 --> 58:27.285
Oh, no problem. Just a nervous breakdown.

58:28.291 --> 58:30.589
[Gasps]

58:30.627 --> 58:32.060
Mary Heller?

58:32.095 --> 58:33.687
My name's Simon Sheppard.

58:33.730 --> 58:35.220
I'm here about your father.

58:35.265 --> 58:36.698
My father?

58:38.468 --> 58:41.437
Who are you? How did you find me?

58:41.471 --> 58:43.132
Is there somewhere we could speak?

58:45.275 --> 58:48.244
My father and I have not had contact in over 12 years.

58:48.278 --> 58:51.543
I assure you it's not because I can't remember the address.

58:51.581 --> 58:53.344
SIMON: Whatever you may think about him...

58:53.383 --> 58:55.613
you only know the half of it.

58:55.652 --> 58:57.119
Look, this is not a good time for me.

58:57.153 --> 58:59.781
In fact, it's a really, really bad time.

58:59.823 --> 59:01.814
[Elevator door opens]

59:04.427 --> 59:05.758
I have to go.

59:07.263 --> 59:08.992
Mary, I'm here to help you.

59:11.735 --> 59:13.600
Mary, I know about your mother.

59:13.636 --> 59:17.231
How she took you off to Scotland, Canada, here.

59:17.273 --> 59:19.741
She never told you the reason, did she?

59:19.776 --> 59:22.574
I saw what it did to her.

59:22.612 --> 59:24.409
[Bottle rolling]

59:25.949 --> 59:27.416
But...

59:27.450 --> 59:29.247
Mary...

59:30.487 --> 59:32.921
Mary, what you're scared of is real.

59:32.956 --> 59:36.483
Your father's the only one who can help you.

59:36.526 --> 59:39.791
MARCUS: Buy a brother a drink?

59:39.829 --> 59:41.694
Sorry, mate.

59:54.077 --> 59:55.977
[Chuckles]

59:56.012 --> 59:58.344
I've been following you all night.

59:58.381 --> 01:00:01.282
[Grunting]

01:00:04.154 --> 01:00:05.712
You!

01:00:07.057 --> 01:00:08.456
You got me thinkin'.

01:00:16.533 --> 01:00:17.727
MARCUS: How's this for a concept?

01:00:20.203 --> 01:00:22.068
Eye for an eye, mate!

01:00:22.105 --> 01:00:23.072
[Sizzling]

01:00:23.106 --> 01:00:24.471
Aah! Damn it!

01:00:24.507 --> 01:00:26.668
Ow!

01:00:48.698 --> 01:00:53.192
Never, ever fuck with an antiques dealer.

01:01:03.546 --> 01:01:06.344
[Growling]

01:01:14.657 --> 01:01:16.852
[Body falls]

01:01:44.320 --> 01:01:46.117
VAN HELSING: Mary?

01:01:46.156 --> 01:01:48.147
[Banging]

01:02:11.314 --> 01:02:14.442
DRACULA: Abraham Van Helsing.

01:02:17.987 --> 01:02:21.286
DRACULA: Beaten by your own reflection.

01:02:25.795 --> 01:02:30.095
You can't have her...ever!

01:02:30.133 --> 01:02:31.327
Can't I?

01:02:31.367 --> 01:02:32.857
VAN HELSING: If you harm my daughter...

01:02:32.902 --> 01:02:35.769
I swear to the Lord Christ--

01:02:35.805 --> 01:02:37.329
Shh!

01:02:37.373 --> 01:02:39.534
He doesn't care.

01:02:39.576 --> 01:02:41.771
In that you can trust.

01:02:41.811 --> 01:02:46.441
You stole life from my blood...

01:02:46.482 --> 01:02:49.315
and passed it to another.

01:02:49.352 --> 01:02:52.321
She's my Mary now.

01:02:52.355 --> 01:02:54.915
Never. Never.

01:02:54.958 --> 01:02:56.482
You want revenge, take it.

01:02:56.526 --> 01:02:58.221
Right here, right now!

01:02:58.261 --> 01:03:01.355
You know not the depths of my vengeance.

01:03:14.310 --> 01:03:16.278
[Children playing]

01:03:16.312 --> 01:03:18.007
BOY: Who's it?

01:03:29.959 --> 01:03:31.950
[Rumbling]

01:03:32.962 --> 01:03:34.452
Lucy?

01:03:35.698 --> 01:03:38.531
[Telephone rings]

01:03:40.637 --> 01:03:42.400
[Ring]

01:03:43.506 --> 01:03:44.939
Hello?

01:03:44.974 --> 01:03:47.067
LUCY: Hey, Mare. It's me.

01:03:47.110 --> 01:03:50.841
[Sighs] Lucy.

01:03:50.880 --> 01:03:52.438
Where are you?

01:03:52.482 --> 01:03:55.451
LUCY: I'm with your father.

01:03:58.187 --> 01:04:00.246
What did you say?

01:04:00.290 --> 01:04:02.758
LUCY: Ahh...

01:04:04.027 --> 01:04:08.760
Lucy, where are you right now?

01:04:08.798 --> 01:04:11.494
LUCY: Where do you think?

01:04:12.635 --> 01:04:14.626
[Dial tone]

01:04:16.272 --> 01:04:18.570
[Beeping dial tone]

01:04:18.608 --> 01:04:20.599
[Rumbling]

01:04:52.909 --> 01:04:55.537
[Telephone off the hook]

01:04:58.915 --> 01:05:01.008
[Beeping dial tone]

01:05:26.518 --> 01:05:28.110
Aah!

01:05:31.689 --> 01:05:34.214
[Beeping dial tone]

01:05:59.317 --> 01:06:01.046
Luce?

01:06:55.039 --> 01:06:57.098
Father?

01:07:20.431 --> 01:07:22.262
[Line ringing]

01:07:22.300 --> 01:07:24.291
[Beeping dial tone]

01:07:26.237 --> 01:07:28.262
You had him every night in your dreams...

01:07:28.306 --> 01:07:31.036
and you never even shared.

01:07:32.210 --> 01:07:34.735
It is better than chocolate.

01:07:34.779 --> 01:07:36.440
[Hisses]

01:07:54.732 --> 01:07:55.892
Aah!

01:07:55.933 --> 01:07:57.298
Oh! Oh, my--

01:08:00.238 --> 01:08:02.536
So, what makes you the one?

01:08:02.573 --> 01:08:05.599
What do you have that we don't have?

01:08:07.945 --> 01:08:09.276
SOLINA: Oh, I know.

01:08:12.483 --> 01:08:14.314
SOLINA: Let's see what we have.

01:08:14.352 --> 01:08:16.149
Oh, yes.

01:08:16.187 --> 01:08:17.711
No.

01:08:17.755 --> 01:08:20.986
SOLINA: Yeah, I can still taste it on your daddy's blood.

01:08:21.024 --> 01:08:24.620
VALERIE: Oh, yes. The essence.

01:08:24.662 --> 01:08:26.459
[Hissing]

01:08:26.497 --> 01:08:29.466
What he took from Dracula, he passed on to you.

01:08:29.500 --> 01:08:31.229
SOLINA: Born with his blood...

01:08:31.269 --> 01:08:34.067
but not like the rest of us.

01:08:34.104 --> 01:08:36.573
Daddy's little prodigal.

01:08:36.607 --> 01:08:38.631
VALERIE: Sorry about your old man.

01:08:38.676 --> 01:08:40.337
We sucked him dry.

01:08:40.377 --> 01:08:42.140
[Valerie laughing]

01:08:42.180 --> 01:08:43.238
Rahrr!

01:09:15.046 --> 01:09:16.979
[Hissing]

01:09:17.014 --> 01:09:18.002
[Thunder]

01:09:29.794 --> 01:09:31.819
[Wolf growling]

01:09:38.636 --> 01:09:39.660
Get down!

01:09:46.310 --> 01:09:48.301
[Screeching]

01:09:50.413 --> 01:09:53.349
You all right? You OK? Yeah?

01:09:54.385 --> 01:09:57.252
Where's your father?

01:09:57.288 --> 01:09:59.222
Where is he?

01:10:09.500 --> 01:10:12.333
MARY: "My unholy addiction has corrupted Mary's blood...

01:10:12.370 --> 01:10:13.359
"and not a day goes by...

01:10:13.404 --> 01:10:15.895
"that I don't pray for her mortal soul.

01:10:15.940 --> 01:10:19.034
MARY: "Yesterday, her mother discovered my secret.

01:10:19.076 --> 01:10:21.943
"I know now that I shall never see...

01:10:21.979 --> 01:10:25.676
"either my wife or daughter again.

01:10:25.716 --> 01:10:27.843
"Perhaps it's for the best...

01:10:27.885 --> 01:10:31.412
"but the pain of their loss is unendurable."

01:10:35.426 --> 01:10:37.621
MARY: "Still, I must carry on."

01:10:40.665 --> 01:10:42.257
You knew about this?

01:10:42.300 --> 01:10:45.201
Not until tonight.

01:10:45.236 --> 01:10:46.533
So, what now, Simon?

01:10:46.571 --> 01:10:49.404
SIMON: We need a sacred place. Somewhere to hide till dawn.

01:10:49.440 --> 01:10:50.634
We'll figure this out.

01:10:50.675 --> 01:10:54.406
There's an old seminary nearby with a church.

01:10:54.445 --> 01:10:56.538
MARY: We can go there.

01:11:07.258 --> 01:11:09.886
MARY: So, I'm part of him.

01:11:09.927 --> 01:11:14.762
His blood. I'm part of Dracula.

01:11:16.601 --> 01:11:18.660
It's what all this is about, isn't it?

01:11:20.838 --> 01:11:22.499
I'm his.

01:11:24.709 --> 01:11:27.075
Since the moment I was born.

01:11:27.111 --> 01:11:29.238
SIMON: No, Mary. You're not his...

01:11:29.280 --> 01:11:31.305
and you never will be.

01:11:33.818 --> 01:11:36.446
I won't let that happen.

01:11:38.656 --> 01:11:41.090
Why are you doing this?

01:11:48.099 --> 01:11:50.590
Well, let's just say...

01:11:50.635 --> 01:11:52.660
I made a pretty fair mess of things...

01:11:52.703 --> 01:11:54.830
before your father came along.

01:11:56.173 --> 01:11:58.107
I was out of control, and he gave me a job...

01:11:58.142 --> 01:11:59.837
turned my life around.

01:12:00.845 --> 01:12:03.609
Now I can never pay him back.

01:12:05.049 --> 01:12:08.212
Except, maybe, by doing right by you.

01:12:13.090 --> 01:12:15.752
Or maybe I would've done it anyway.

01:12:20.420 --> 01:12:23.947
Do you believe in destiny, Simon?

01:12:23.990 --> 01:12:25.457
Fate?

01:12:25.492 --> 01:12:28.256
Your father kept us all safe from this evil...

01:12:28.295 --> 01:12:30.627
for a hundred years.

01:12:32.165 --> 01:12:33.496
He defied death to do it.

01:12:33.533 --> 01:12:37.230
Something tells me he didn't ask fate for permission.

01:12:37.270 --> 01:12:39.033
Well, I'm not my father.

01:12:39.072 --> 01:12:41.939
Don't be so sure.

01:12:46.913 --> 01:12:49.507
Wait.

01:12:49.549 --> 01:12:52.347
This might be of some use.

01:12:56.056 --> 01:12:58.490
Point and pray.

01:13:01.361 --> 01:13:03.352
SIMON: Modern legends all date back...

01:13:03.396 --> 01:13:06.160
to the 15th Century warlord Dracula.

01:13:06.199 --> 01:13:10.659
MARY: Father kept him locked up in some kind of dungeon?

01:13:10.704 --> 01:13:12.729
SIMON: He tried to keep him from the world, Mary...

01:13:12.772 --> 01:13:15.866
but most of all, he tried to keep him from you.

01:13:15.909 --> 01:13:18.207
SIMON: He was trying to find a way...

01:13:18.244 --> 01:13:19.871
to kill an immortal being.

01:13:19.913 --> 01:13:22.313
SIMON: He knew that Dracula was just one of his many names.

01:13:22.349 --> 01:13:23.748
He knew he had to be much older than that...

01:13:23.783 --> 01:13:27.480
and the answer may lie hidden in the historical record.

01:13:27.520 --> 01:13:31.854
MARY: Maybe the only way to know death, Simon...

01:13:31.891 --> 01:13:35.327
is to...embrace it.

01:13:35.362 --> 01:13:37.387
You can't think like that.

01:13:39.199 --> 01:13:41.167
You can't.

01:13:44.304 --> 01:13:46.499
We know he detests all things Christian...

01:13:46.539 --> 01:13:49.997
SIMON: holy water, the Cross, the Bible.

01:13:50.043 --> 01:13:51.510
And silver.

01:13:51.544 --> 01:13:53.535
SIMON: Why silver? It's not uniquely Christian.

01:13:53.580 --> 01:13:55.946
Has to be something more.

01:13:58.084 --> 01:13:59.210
SIMON: Something personal.

01:13:59.252 --> 01:14:01.880
MARY: Wait. He wrote something like that.

01:14:02.889 --> 01:14:04.186
At my house.

01:14:04.224 --> 01:14:06.192
- Is that Hebrew?
- Aramaic.

01:14:06.226 --> 01:14:08.524
Aramaic?

01:14:08.561 --> 01:14:11.428
That's been a dead language for almost 2,000 years.

01:14:11.464 --> 01:14:16.299
MARY: "Believe in me, for I am the way to...

01:14:16.336 --> 01:14:19.863
"to eternity."

01:14:19.906 --> 01:14:21.464
You know Aramaic?

01:14:21.508 --> 01:14:24.705
No, but he does.

01:14:24.744 --> 01:14:26.041
[Boom]

01:14:42.028 --> 01:14:43.825
Simon?

01:14:47.133 --> 01:14:49.567
Propaganda.

01:14:49.602 --> 01:14:51.900
MARY: Simon. Wait.

01:14:51.938 --> 01:14:53.235
SIMON: Run, Mary!

01:14:53.273 --> 01:14:54.763
Get out of here now!

01:14:59.179 --> 01:15:03.843
DRACULA: You think you can defend her with the Bible?

01:15:19.766 --> 01:15:21.791
[Bell chiming]

01:15:59.672 --> 01:16:02.163
[Whoosh]

01:16:35.942 --> 01:16:37.273
[Gasps]

01:16:47.353 --> 01:16:48.342
Mary!

01:16:50.089 --> 01:16:51.386
[Gasps]

01:16:58.565 --> 01:17:03.298
DRACULA: I have walked the earth for centuries...

01:17:03.336 --> 01:17:09.434
in search of a soul not bitten, but born.

01:17:09.475 --> 01:17:11.739
I am not like you.

01:17:11.778 --> 01:17:15.646
Everything I am is yours.

01:17:15.682 --> 01:17:17.980
Mary!

01:17:18.017 --> 01:17:20.042
Mary!

01:17:20.086 --> 01:17:21.713
SIMON: Mary!

01:17:21.754 --> 01:17:26.453
And all you are is mine.

01:17:30.330 --> 01:17:31.524
SIMON: Mary!

01:17:44.143 --> 01:17:45.269
Uhh!

01:17:48.548 --> 01:17:51.016
[Crowd yelling]

01:17:56.055 --> 01:17:58.046
[Man singing indistinctly]

01:18:06.866 --> 01:18:08.356
MAN: Over here!

01:18:16.509 --> 01:18:18.170
Hey, take your shirt off!

01:18:31.190 --> 01:18:33.215
[Hisses]

01:18:33.259 --> 01:18:34.726
Shit.

01:19:01.020 --> 01:19:02.647
LUCY: Ah, simple Simon.

01:19:02.689 --> 01:19:04.316
Aah!

01:19:06.526 --> 01:19:07.993
[Hisses]

01:19:09.162 --> 01:19:10.356
VALERIE: So tell me...

01:19:10.396 --> 01:19:13.688
did you ever dream about making it with a TV star?

01:19:13.821 --> 01:19:16.187
[Valerie laughs]

01:19:37.512 --> 01:19:39.980
Oh, Simon, why fight it?

01:19:40.014 --> 01:19:42.414
Mary's his.

01:19:42.450 --> 01:19:44.475
She belongs to him.

01:19:44.519 --> 01:19:46.146
No.

01:19:46.187 --> 01:19:48.985
We'll all be lovers soon.

01:19:49.023 --> 01:19:50.547
No. Unh!

01:19:52.760 --> 01:19:54.091
Aah!

01:20:19.620 --> 01:20:25.149
You cannot imagine what I've had to endure.

01:20:25.193 --> 01:20:29.129
DRACULA: I have borne the very wrath of God.

01:20:31.899 --> 01:20:36.268
Chosen to suffer like no man before.

01:20:36.304 --> 01:20:38.772
Who are you?

01:20:42.643 --> 01:20:46.044
DRACULA: It was my last sunset on this earth...

01:20:46.080 --> 01:20:49.140
that made me who I am.

01:20:51.285 --> 01:20:53.947
Let me show you...

01:20:53.988 --> 01:20:57.617
what I have shown no other.

01:21:31.125 --> 01:21:33.116
[Woman singing]

01:21:39.434 --> 01:21:41.527
Blood of my blood...

01:21:43.538 --> 01:21:46.803
flesh of my flesh.

01:21:51.479 --> 01:21:53.777
[Thunder]

01:22:30.785 --> 01:22:32.582
Judas Iscariot.

01:22:33.721 --> 01:22:37.589
The cross, the silver...

01:22:37.625 --> 01:22:40.185
all the things you came to despise.

01:22:54.942 --> 01:22:56.466
[Gasps]

01:23:02.884 --> 01:23:06.411
DRACULA: You knew this would come to pass.

01:23:06.454 --> 01:23:10.083
It was my destiny to betray you...

01:23:10.124 --> 01:23:13.525
because you needed me.

01:23:20.134 --> 01:23:22.398
Now...

01:23:22.436 --> 01:23:26.770
I drink the blood of your children...

01:23:26.807 --> 01:23:29.708
but I give them more than just eternal life.

01:23:29.744 --> 01:23:33.077
I give them what they crave most.

01:23:36.918 --> 01:23:40.445
All the pleasure you would deny them...

01:23:42.056 --> 01:23:43.318
forever.

01:23:46.994 --> 01:23:48.985
[Laughs]

01:23:53.000 --> 01:23:56.367
DRACULA: You made the world in your image...

01:23:56.404 --> 01:23:57.894
but now...

01:23:59.240 --> 01:24:01.731
I make it in mine.

01:24:07.982 --> 01:24:09.609
Come, Mary.

01:24:09.650 --> 01:24:12.676
DRACULA: Let us feast.

01:24:37.545 --> 01:24:39.672
She's one of us now.

01:24:39.714 --> 01:24:41.204
You can smell it on her.

01:24:41.249 --> 01:24:43.774
We've saved him for you, Mary.

01:24:43.818 --> 01:24:47.276
DRACULA: Show him there is nothing to fear.

01:24:49.991 --> 01:24:51.856
Blood...

01:24:51.892 --> 01:24:55.885
has always been the coin of our realm.

01:25:09.176 --> 01:25:11.736
Save some for us, Mare.

01:25:17.752 --> 01:25:20.653
SIMON: No, Mary, please.

01:25:22.390 --> 01:25:24.017
Mary, don't.

01:25:25.426 --> 01:25:27.018
Please.

01:25:29.964 --> 01:25:31.556
Aah! Aah!

01:25:53.454 --> 01:25:55.183
Thanks, Luce.

01:25:57.625 --> 01:25:59.286
Hey...

01:26:13.441 --> 01:26:15.739
I'd like his head.

01:26:15.776 --> 01:26:19.403
Vampire or not, he won't stop hunting us now.

01:26:26.477 --> 01:26:28.775
He's yours to end.

01:26:44.061 --> 01:26:46.222
Oh, Simon.

01:26:57.007 --> 01:26:58.736
Bitch is faking it.

01:26:58.776 --> 01:26:59.868
No!

01:27:03.914 --> 01:27:05.245
For my father.

01:27:06.450 --> 01:27:07.576
Go!

01:27:23.767 --> 01:27:26.600
You think you can teach me about betrayal?

01:27:50.894 --> 01:27:53.624
Didn't your father ever tell you, Mary?

01:27:53.664 --> 01:27:56.531
I can't die. He won't have me.

01:27:56.567 --> 01:27:57.864
Did you ever ask?

01:27:57.901 --> 01:28:00.267
For what? Forgiveness?

01:28:03.307 --> 01:28:06.470
You really think I'd go back to him? Never!

01:28:12.316 --> 01:28:14.216
[Click]

